⏳ Ping of this shard is **<[0]>ms**.
Average ping of all shard is **<[1]>ms**
UnsupportLanguage: Language to change was not defined or not Support language.
SupportLanguageList: I can speak with Korean **(ko)** and English **(en)**!
changedLanguageWith: Language has changed to <[0]>. From now on, I will speak in the changed language!
howtochangelang_solution:
You can change language with type ``<[0]>lang {language_code_here}``
Example : ``<[0]>lang ko``
tip_desc: You can see each command's description by send `<[0]>help <command>`
support_desc:
To report bug and issue, or if you want chat with other bot users, join support discord server!
https://discord.gg/Ar4ut2W
cmd_invite_desc:
Show Bot's invite link.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>invite``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>초대``
cmd_support_desc:
Show bot's support server link.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>support``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>지원``
cmd_ping_desc:
Show Bot's ping.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>ping``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>핑``, ``<[0]>퐁``, ``<[0]>pong``
cmd_help_desc:
Show Bot's help message. (Like this message that you are reading!)
Usage:
> ``<[0]>help (command)``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>도움``, ``<[0]>도움말``, ``<[0]>manual``
cmd_lang_desc:
Change Bot's language that react for you!
Usage:
> ``<[0]>lang <language code>``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>lang``, ``<[0]>language``
cmd_reboot_desc:
Reboot All shards of bot.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>reboot``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>재시동``, ``<[0]>재시작``, ``<[0]>restart``
cmd_shell_desc:
Run command to remote bot server.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>shell <code to compile>``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>command``, ``<[0]>code``
cmd_compile_desc:
Run JS code to remote bot server.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>compile <command to run>``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>eval``
cmd_notice_desc:
Send notice message to all server.
Usage:
> ``<[0]>notice <message>``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>공지``
cmd_sayd_desc:
Repeat your message!
Usage:
> ``<[0]>sayd <Message to send>``
Same featured command:
> ``<[0]>따라해``
